parameters.name: thd_psef_data_quality

parameters.name: thd_psef_en_efluxQ
parameters.description: SST Electron energy spectrogram(Good data only). This variable is a 'virtual' variable that is computed using the function apply_esa_qflag (see https://cdaweb.gsfc.nasa.gov/pub/software/cdawlib/source/virtual_funcs.pro) on the with inputs of the variables ['thd_psef_en_eflux', 'thd_psef_data_quality'].
